      "title": "One-hour power cut until Friday: PUCSL",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) today approved power cuts of 1 hour from tomorrow (6) until Friday (9).",
        "Accordingly, the areas under the groups A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K, L, P, Q, R, S, T, U, V and W will face a one-hour powercut between 6 p.m. and\u00a0 9 p.m. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
